highlights.text: “Jaane Kyu Main” by Prashant Katheriya is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Patna, up 22 spots at #75.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Patna. “Kesariya” is the highest at #2.
“Basti Ka Hasti” by MC STAN is the highest new entry on Top Songs Patna at #83.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Patna the longest, at 61 weeks straight.
